    {\displaystyle \delta ^{ij}}
  , which is just a tensor equivalent of the identity matrix, and 
  
    
      
        
          δ
          
            i
            j
          
        
        =
        
          δ
          
            i
            j
          
        
        =
        
          δ
          
            j
          
          
            i
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \delta _{ij}=\delta ^{ij}=\delta _{j}^{i}}
  .

